Package fr.sorbonne_u.devs_simulation.hioa.annotations

Annotations for HIOA DEVS models.

See: Description

  • Annotation Types Summary 
    Annotation Type Description
    ExportedVariable
    The annotation ExportedVariable declares that a variable values are computed by the HIOA atomic model declaring the variable.
    ImportedVariable
    The annotation ImportedVariable declares that a variable values are consumed by the HIOA atomic model declaring the variable.
    InternalVariable
    The annotation InternalVariable declares that a variable values are local to the HIOA atomic model declaring the variable.

Package fr.sorbonne_u.devs_simulation.hioa.annotations Description

Annotations for HIOA DEVS models.

This package defines annotations for HIOA models in simulation architectures. They are meant to provide information about the models used by the model composition process (at composition time) giving composed DEVS models ready to be executed.
